26:40.641 --> 26:41.756
Alcide.

26:41.934 --> 26:43.470
Marcus.

26:43.644 --> 26:46.431
-I'm glad to see you here.
-Glad to be here.

26:46.605 --> 26:48.641
-Debbie.
-Hey.

26:50.442 --> 26:54.310
