Those witches attacked you...

35:56.154 --> 35:58.315
...and other vampires I care about.

35:59.407 --> 36:03.491
-My king?
-Yes, your king...

36:03.662 --> 36:05.903
...who released you
so you could be with me.

36:06.081 --> 36:08.163
He's good, this king.

36:10.251 --> 36:11.707
I understand your love for him.

36:11.920 --> 36:15.162
We have an obligation to stand by his side
and fight with him.

36:15.340 --> 36:18.082
No, the obligation is his.

36:18.259 --> 36:20.341
As king, he has no choice.

36:20.512 --> 36:23.219
Let's just leave this place
while we still can.

36:23.431 --> 36:29.142
This is my home,
and we cannotjust leave Bill to die.

36:29.312 --> 36:34.648
-It's not right.
-There is no right or wrong.

36:35.735 --> 36:37.316
These are human notions.

36:37.487 --> 36:41.025
And I am human, mostly.

36:41.199 --> 36:43.611
And so were you,
and I've never seen you as human...

36:43.785 --> 36:45.696
...as you've been these past few days.

36:45.870 --> 36:48.452
It's what I've fallen in love with.

36:48.998 --> 36:53.958
But you're also a warrior
and you don't run from a fight.

36:54.129 --> 36:55.915
You'd never forgive yourself.

36:56.089 --> 36:58.705
I just want to be with you.

36:59.384 --> 37:01.249
Only you.

37:02.637 --> 37:04.377
Forever.

37:05.515 --> 37:08.552
There's no such thing as forever.

37:20.655 --> 37:22.737
Hey. I'm just calling
to give you a heads-up.

37:22.907 --> 37:25.364
I'm gonna stop by,
tuck my baby girl in, okay?

37:31.916 --> 37:33.201
-You heading out?
ALCIDE: Yeah.

37:33.376 --> 37:36.038
I got a foundation to pour
first thing in the morning.

37:36.212 --> 37:37.918
Well, you two get home safe.

37:38.089 --> 37:41.798
Word is something big is going down
tonight with the witches and vampires.

37:42.886 --> 37:45.719
