not control.

37:57.358 --> 38:01.351
-It's honorable.
-Yep. That's him.

38:01.529 --> 38:05.613
-You can move up in this pack.
-Well, I ain't into the whole political thing.

38:05.784 --> 38:08.617
Okay. You got your own path.

38:08.787 --> 38:11.324
I'm just saying, door's open.

38:11.748 --> 38:13.613
-Good night.
DEBBIE: See you.

38:16.252 --> 38:19.995
-I think we're gonna like being in this pack.
-Yeah, it's too soon to tell.

38:20.173 --> 38:21.834
DEBBIE:
Oh, come on.

38:22.008 --> 38:25.967
You remember how good
things were in Jackson when we were kids?

38:26.930 --> 38:29.797
Everyone looked out for each other.

38:30.475 --> 38:33.808
Being in a pack could be a good thing,
you know, for us both.

38:33.978 --> 38:36.811
-Maybe.
-I need this, Alcide.

38:37.565 --> 38:39.977
It's a miracle I'm not dead.

38:40.318 --> 38:43.481
You know, but I got a second chance,
and I don't want to screw it up.

38:43.655 --> 38:45.395
But you gotta help me.

38:45.573 --> 38:47.985
-Of course.
-You gotta stay away from Sookie.

38:48.159 --> 38:51.651
-I told you, you got nothing to worry about.
-You're a member of this pack.

38:51.830 --> 38:53.821
And Marcus was crystal clear.

38:54.249 --> 38:56.991
We stay the fuck out
of that vampire-witch business.

38:57.168 --> 39:02.208
And Sookie comes with vampires.
That's just part of her baggage.

39:03.633 --> 39:05.089
Can't argue with that.

39:05.260 --> 39:06.420
You promise?

39:08.012 --> 39:10.173
You'll stay away from her?

39:13.810 --> 39:15.095
I promise.

39:24.237 --> 39:25.443
Come on.

39:42.839 --> 39:45.421
