Where my sister?

40:06.821 --> 40:08.652
I sent her home.

40:09.949 --> 40:11.234
Mavis, don't go in there.

40:11.826 --> 40:14.238
-My baby. I want my baby, me.
-Mavis, please.

40:14.412 --> 40:16.653
I buy him this doll. I save all my moneys.

40:17.040 --> 40:19.577
