-And I work for my wife's father.
-Please just bring me where he is.

41:13.304 --> 41:17.468
-Can't bear it. Can't--
-Please. Just let me hold him one last--

41:17.642 --> 41:20.930
PIe-- Just let me hold him.

41:21.104 --> 41:23.095
[SOBBING]

41:29.487 --> 41:31.569
Huh?

41:31.739 --> 41:33.650
Oh, fuck, no.

41:36.577 --> 41:38.317
[GRUNTING]

41:52.385 --> 41:54.125
[HUMMING]

42:28.546 --> 42:33.836
Sorry to keep you waiting, and I don't
have much time, so, what can I do for you?

42:34.010 --> 42:36.717
-We're here to fight with you.
-Fight with me?

42:37.346 --> 42:38.472
Against the witches.

42:39.515 --> 42:43.758
-Sookie, this is not your battle.
-It's yours and it's Eric's, so it's mine.

42:43.936 --> 42:46.063
She has a warrior's heart, Your Majesty.

42:46.731 --> 42:50.223
She wants to fight for you, as do I.

42:50.401 --> 42:52.687
-I want peace.
-But you're prepared for war.

42:52.862 --> 42:55.274
Of course.
But I'm not convinced we will win.

42:55.448 --> 42:58.030
Well, war isn't about
whether you think you can win.

42:58.201 --> 43:01.910
It's about being willing to die for
something you believe is worth dying for.

43:02.080 --> 43:05.117
Perhaps I'm less inclined to gamble
with Sookie's life than you.

43:05.333 --> 43:06.823
That is not our decision.

43:07.001 --> 43:08.207
Thank you, Eric.

43:08.377 --> 43:12.336
And now maybe you can both look at me
and allow me to speak for myself.

43:13.591 --> 43:14.922
I can help.

43:15.093 --> 43:18.802
I have powers. Now, granted I may not be
in perfect control of those powers...

43:18.971 --> 43:23.214
...but they've saved me and others
from some pretty dire circumstances.

43:24.477 --> 43:26.263
-Sookie, you could die.
SOOKIE: Well...

43:26.437 --> 43:30.430
...call me crazy, but I'm willing to die if it
means keeping an entire group of people...

43:30.608 --> 43:33.645
